 "Enter LAN MAC   : <6 octects of MAC address with : separator e.g. aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:f0 >\n"
 "Enter WAN-1 MAC : <6 octects of MAC address with : separator e.g. aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:f1 >\n"
